rview%26quot%3B%20that%20Anthropic%20published%20in%20July%2C%20the%20company%20said%20users%20interacting%20with%20Claude%2C%20its%20chatbot%2C%20should%20think%20of%20it%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20brilliant%2C%20but%20very%20new%20employee%20(with%20amnesia)%20who%20needs%20explicit%20instructions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BClaude%20does%20not%20have%20context%20on%20your%20norms%2C%20styles%2C%20guidelines%2C%20or%20preferred%20ways%20of%20working.%20The%20more%20precisely%20you%20explain%20what%20you%20want%2C%20the%20better%20Claude's%20response%20will%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20Anthropic%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVeteran%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarc-andreessen-how-to-prompt-ai-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eventure%20capitalist%20Marc%20Andreessen%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20last%20month%20that%20the%20power%20of%20AI%20comes%20from%20treating%20it%20as%20a%26quot%3Bthought%20partner.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPart%20of%20the%20art%20of%20AI%20is%20what%20questions%20to%20ask%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20who%20master%20this%20skill%20can%20land%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprompt-engineering-ai-chatgpt-jobs-explained-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elucrative%20jobs%20as%20prompt%20engineers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20have%20a%20median%20salary%20of%20%24150%2C000%2C%20according%20to%20levels.fyi%2C%20a%20platform%20for%20tech%20workers%20to%20research%20and%20compare%20salaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-philosopher-amanda-askell-tips-ai-prompting-whispering-claude-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1765046530000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69334dd17ecd1d1da6630f50%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-philosopher-amanda-askell-tips-ai-pro