%20in%20a%20fun%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20Merry%20Little%20Ex-Mas%26quot%3B%20stars%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falicia-silverstone-vegan-diet-miracle-health-asthma-plant-based-vegetarian-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAlicia%20Silverstone%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20Kate%2C%20an%20architect%20turned%20stay-at-home%20mom%20(and%20handyman%2C%20for%20some%20reason)%2C%20who%20is%20recently%20separated%20from%20her%20husband%2C%20Everett%20(Oliver%20Hudson)%2C%20their%20small%20town's%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20many%20choices%20in%20this%20were%20baffling.%20For%20instance%2C%20everyone%20in%20the%20town%20calls%20Kate's%20house%20the%20%26quot%3BMothership.%26quot%3B%20Why%3F%20It%20doesn't%20matter%20%E2%80%94%20it%20never%20gets%20explained.%20Kate%20and%20Everett's%20daughter%2C%20Sienna%2C%20brings%20home%20her%20British%20boyfriend%2C%20who%20inexplicably%20thinks%20he's%20a%20character%20in%20%26quot%3BHarry%20Potter%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20is%20a%20bit%20dated%20in%202025.%20Fellow%20'90s%20queen%20Melissa%20Joan%20Hart%20is%20in%20this%20movie%20for%20around%205%20minutes%2C%20and%20it%20was%2C%20frankly%2C%20rude%20not%20to%20give%20her%20more%20to%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20movie's%20saving%20grace%20was%20Kate's%20much%20younger%20boyfriend%2C%20Chet%2C%20played%20by%20Pierson%20Fod%C3%A9%2C%20who%20was%20hilarious.%20Everett's%20new%20girlfriend%2C%20Tess%2C%20played%20by%20Jameela%20Jamil%2C%20also%20brought%20a%20lot%20of%20laughs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20romance%20between%20Kate%20and%20Everett%20just%20wasn't%20explored%20enough.%20From%20the%20first%20scene%20they're%20in%20together%2C%20it's%20clear%20there%20was%20no%20reason%20to%20split%20up%20in%20the%20first%20place%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0they%20needed%20some%20couple's%20therapy%20and%20to%20work%20on%20their%20communication%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20want%20better%20for%20two%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F90s-singers-then-and-now-2017-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E'90s%20legends%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E2.%20%26quot%3BChampagne%20Problems%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225759%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22champagne%20problems%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6931b42e7ecd1d1da662ed77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224319%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BChampagne%20Problems.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EMika%20Cotellon%2FNetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESue%20me%2C%20I%20thought%20this%20was%20cute!%20Any%20movie%20that%20takes%20place%20in%20Paris%20during%20Christmas%20is%20going%20to%20earn%20extra%20points%20with%20me%2C%20it's%20just%20a%20fact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChampagne%20Problems%26quot%3B%20stars%20Minka%20Kelly%20as%20Sydney%2C%20a%20dedicated%20employee%20at%20her%20mergers%20and%20acquisitions%20firm%2C%20but%20who%20has%20no%20life%20of%20her%20own.%20When%20she%20gets%20sent%20to%20Paris%20right%20around%20Christmas%20to%20pitch%20an%20acquisition%20of%20a%20local%20Champagne%20brand%2C%20she%20takes%20one%20night%20for%20herself%20and%20meets%20Henri%20(Tom%20Wozniczka%3Cu%3E)%3C%2Fu%3E.%20Can%20you%20see%20where%20this%20is%20going%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20of%20course%2C%20Henri%20is%20the%20son%20of%20the%20man%20whose%20business%20Sydney%20wants%20to%20take%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Sydney's%20not%20the%20only%20one%20competing%20for%20the%20chateau's%20business.%20There%20are%20a%20few%20pleasantly%20kooky%20side%20characters%20who%20are%20along%20for%20the%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20main%20takeaway%20from%20this%20movie%20is%20that%20I%20should%20probably%20book%20a%20flight%20to%20Paris%20immediately%20(I%20also%20frantically%20Googled%20if%20the%20bookstore%20in%20the%20movie%20was%20real.%20It's%20not%2C%20sadly).%20My%20secondary%20thoughts%20include%20that%20Kelly%20and%20Wozniczka%20have%20great%20chemistry%2C%20and%20I%20need%20to%20pop%20a%20bottle%20of%20bubbly%20this%20Christmas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E1.%20%26quot%3BJingle%20Bell%20Heist%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225365%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jingle%20bell%20heist%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6931ef6a04d0f0a114f1701c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BJingle%20Bell%20Heist.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ERob%20Baker%20Ashton%2FNetflix%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20an%20easy%20choice.%20%26quot%3BJingle%20Bell%20Heist%26quot%3B%20is%20the%20only%20one%20of%20these%20movies%20that%20didn't%20have%20an%20overly%20bright%2C%20but%20somehow%20still%20flat%2C%20aesthetic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20stars%20two%20promising%20young%20actors%2C%20Olivia%20Holt%20and%20Connor%20Swindells.%20Holt%20plays%20Sophie%2C%20an%20American%20living%20in%20London%20so%20her%20mom%20can%20access%20cheaper%20cancer%20treatment%20%E2%80%94%20Sophie%20is%20also%20a%20star%20pick-pocket%20who%20learned%20everything%20she%20knows%20from%20her%20magician%20grandfather%2C%20which%20%E2%80%A6%20sure.%20Swindells%20plays%20Nick%2C%20a%20computer%20expert%20who%20has%20recently%20been%20released%20from%20jail%20after%20being%20accused%20of%20robbing%20a%20department%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENick%20and%20Sophie%20link%20up%20to%20rob%20that%20same%20department%20store%20on%20Christmas%20Eve%20for%20their%20own%20reasons%2C%20but%2C%20of%20course%2C%20things%20never%20go%20smoothly%20in%20a%20film%20like%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20give%20screenwriters%20Abby%20McDonald%20and%20Amy%20Reed%20a%20lot%20of%20credit%2C%20because%20this%20movie%20had%20more%20than%20one%20twist%20that%20genuinely%20shocked%20me.%20I%20also%20vibed%20with%20Michael%20Fimognari's%20direction%2C%20as%20it's%20clear%20he%20was%20doing%20his%20best%20'70s%20crime-thriller%20tribute.%20Lastly%2C%20the%20brassy%20score%20by%20Steve%20Hackman%20was%20great%3B%20it%20was%20giving%20%26quot%3BOcean's%20Eleven.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20one%20knock%20on%20this%20movie%20is%20that%20the%20relationship%20between%20Sophie%20and%20Nick%20was%20pretty%20boring%2C%20all%20things%20considered.%20Perhaps%20they%20just%20had%20better%20platonic%20chemistry%20than%20romantic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20this%20was%20easily%20my%20favorite%20of%20Netflix's%20holiday%20films%20this%20year%2C%20and%20one%20I%20would%20recommend%20to%20anyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-2025-holiday-movies-ranked-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1765031762000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6931fbbb04d0f0a114f17227%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-2025-holiday-movies-ranked-2025-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Netflix%20has%20released%20four%20new%20holiday%20movies%20this%20year%2C%20including%20%26quot%3BJingle%20Bell%20Heist%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BA%20Merry%20Little%20Ex-Mas.%26quot%3B%20See%20which%20ones%20are%20worth%20your%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Gabbi%20Shaw)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-2025-holiday-movies-ranked-2025-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22AceVector%20files%20updated%20IPO%20papers%2C%20targets%20%E2%82%B9300%20crore%20fresh%20issue%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1765031624000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2025-12%2F06%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F1200X630%2F1765031560-7753.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fcompanies-ipo-acevector-updated-ipo-papers-targets-rs-300-crore-fresh-issue-125120600729_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%