%20Philippe%20Jordan%2C%20president%20of%20French%20hedge%20fund%20giant%20%3A%20You%20don't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECulture%20is%20often%20mythologized%2C%20but%2C%20in%20Jordan's%20view%2C%20it%20is%20the%20simple%20byproduct%20of%20past%20shared%20experiences%20at%20its%20core%2C%20and%20he%20warns%20against%20the%20impulse%20to%20lionize%20%26quot%3Bthe%20good%20old%20days.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNostalgia%20turns%20a%20culture%20into%20an%20artifact%2C%20and%20our%20culture%20is%20dynamic%2C%26quot%3B%20Jordan%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECFM%2C%20a%20Paris-based%20quantitative%20multistrategy%20fund%2C%20has%20been%20on%20a%20growth%20tear%20of%20its%20own.%20Assets%20climbed%20roughly%2025%25%20from%20the%20start%20of%20this%20year%20to%20%2421%20billion%20as%20of%20September.%20Five%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20firm%20managed%20just%20%246.5%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHead%20count%20has%20surged%20as%20well%2C%20from%20260%20employees%20at%20the%20end%20of%202020%20to%20nearly%20450%20today.%20CFM's%20New%20York%20office%20has%20doubled%20in%20size%20in%20recent%20years%20to%2040%20people%2C%20including%2015%20researchers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2035-year-old%20firm%20doesn't%20fit%20neatly%20into%20the%20hedge-fund%20typology%2C%20rejecting%20many%20of%20the%20norms%20that%20have%20come%20to%20define%20the%20industry.%20CFM%20has%20no%20larger-than-life%20founder%20that%20reigns%20supreme%3B%20instead%2C%20it's%20governed%20by%20a%20five-member%20board.%20It%20doesn't%20hire%20armies%20of%20independent%20portfolio%20managers.%20Unlike%20most%20of%20its%20quant%20brethren%2C%20it%20isn't%20obsessed%20with%20secrecy.%20And%20it%20doesn't%20espouse%20a%20ruthless%2C%20zero-sum%20mentality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompared%20with%20multimanagers%20that%20dominate%20today's%20hedge-fund%20landscape%2C%20which%20employ%20scores%20of%20siloed%20pods%2C%20CFM%20is%20%26quot%3Bat%20the%20extreme%20other%20end%20of%20the%20spectrum%2C%26quot%3B%20Jordan%20said.%20%26quot%3BLots%20of%20collaboration%2C%20open%20environments%20in%20which%20people%20feel%20free%20to%20communicate%2C%20talk%2C%20and%20be%20curious%20about%20other%20people's%20businesses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECFM%20was%20an%20early%20practitioner%20of%20the%20collegial%2C%20academic%20ethos%20model%20that's%20now%20common%20at%20many%20quant%20trading%20firms.%20Cofounder%20Jean-Pierre%20Aguillar%2C%20an%20engineer%20and%20computer%20scientist%2C%20launched%20CFM%20in%201991%20and%20helped%20define%20the%20firm's%20culture%20before%20his%20death%20in%20a%20gliding%20accident%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20collaboration%20and%20intellectual%20rigor%20is%20prized%2C%20the%20firm%20isn't%20%26quot%3Bthrowing%20spaghetti%20at%20the%20walls.%26quot%3B%20Performance%20matters%20%E2%80%94%20as%20evidenced%20by%20CFM's%20strong%20run%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20win%2C%20but%20not%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20having%20a%20work%20environment%20that's%20not%20sustainable%2C%26quot%3B%20Jordan%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20balance%20has%20helped%20CFM%20maintain%20its%20edge%20and%20attract%20top%20talent%2C%20even%20as%20the%20industry%20shifts%20on%20its%20axis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c57f735a-4790-4d99-a34d-14c980c9c86d%5C%22%3EFrom%20physics%20labs%20to%20trading%20floors%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECFM's%20investment%20engine%20isn't%20driven%20by%20traders%20but%20rather%20academics.%20The%20majority%20of%20recruits%20join%20straight%20out%20of%20PhD%20programs%20%E2%80%94%20typically%20in%20physics%20%E2%80%94%20and%20learn%20finance%20on%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20has%20around%20100%20researchers%2C%20and%20it%20aims%20to%20recruit%2015%20new%20doctorates%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20very%20good%20at%20hiring%20people%20with%20formal%20scientific%20backgrounds%2C%26quot%3B%20Jordan%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20the%20appeal%20is%20the%20feeling%20of%20never%20having%20left%20academia%2C%20despite%20working%20at%20a%20hedge%20fund.%20Most%20hedge%20funds%20shun%20the%20spotlight%2C%20wooing%20top%20mathematicians%20and%20scientists%20with%20the%20understanding%20that%20finance%20riches%20is%20the%20tradeoff%20for%20working%20in%20obscurity.%20Research%20is%20treated%20as%20state%20secrets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20so%20at%20CFM%2C%20where%20researchers%2C%20including%20chairman%20and%20chief%20scientist%20Jean-Philippe%20Bouchaud%2C%20a%20theoretical%20physicist%2C%20regularly%20publish%20academic%20papers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECFM%20isn't%20alone%20%E2%80%94%20firms%20like%20DE%20Shaw%20and%20AQR%20also%20publish%2C%20to%20name%20two%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20isn't%20giving%20away%20valuable%20trading%20signals%2C%20of%20course.%20But%20hundreds%20of%20white%20papers%20have%20emerged%20from%20its%20ranks%20on%20topics%20including%20market%20microstructure%2C%20execution%20costs%2C%20and%20factor%20crowding.%20Researchers%20normally%20present%20their%20work%20in%20weekly%20seminar-style%20meetings%2C%20much%20like%20at%20a%20university.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20be%20at%20CFM%2C%20be%20part%20of%20a%20group%20solving%20problems%20for%20investors%20and%20making%20money%20%E2%80%94%20but%20they're%20also%20publishing%20and%20having%20a%20life%20as%20a%20researcher%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20blend%20of%20intellectual%20freedom%20and%20financial%20upside%20is%20catnip%20for%20the%20PhDs%20CFM%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20CFM%20has%20grown%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20it%20has%20added%20more%20experienced%20hires%20with%20a%20decade%20or%20more%20of%20domain%20expertise.%20Some%20firms%20codify%20culture%20into%20rules%20or%20%26quot%3Bprinciples%26quot%3B%20that%20employees%20are%20expected%20to%20absorb%20and%20emulate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECFM%20takes%20the%20opposite%20view%3A%20newcomers%20should%20respect%20the%20firm's%20collaborative%20ethos%2C%20but%20they're%20also%20expected%20to%20inject%20fresh%20ideas%20and%20entrepreneurial%20verve.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTurning%20people%20into%20CFM%20clones%20is%20not%20a%20good%20idea%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20bring%20those%20people%20in%20because%20they%20know%20things%20that%20we%20don't%2C%20and%20they're%20exposed%20to%20cultures%20that%20we're%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strategy%20has%20been%20working.%20Retention%20remains%20high%2C%20Jordan%20says%2C%20in%20an%20industry%20famous%20for%20burnout%20and%20churn%2C%20with%20many%20researchers%20staying%20close%20to%20a%20decade.%20(CFM%20declined%20to%20provide%20specific%20attrition%20figures.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2223e3d914-d085-4f90-87ea-f1188df40ec4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIncreased%20competition%20in%20Paris%2C%20a%20budding%20quant%20capital%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20doesn't%20mean%20recruitment%20has%20always%20been%20a%20breeze.%20In%20recent%20years%2C%20CFM%20has%20had%20to%20adapt%20to%20an%20onslaught%20of%20new%20competition%20as%20Paris%20has%20evolved%20from%20a%20quant-talent%20exporter%20into%20a%20full-fledged%20hedge-fund%20hub.%20The%20city%20has%20long%20produced%20elite%20mathematical%20minds%20%E2%80%94%20a%20legacy%20of%20its%20rationalist%20tradition%20shaped%20by%20figures%20like%20Ren%C3%A9%20Descartes%20and%20the%20education%20reforms%20of%20Napoleon%20%E2%80%94%20but%20for%20decades%2C%20many%20of%20those%20quants%20left%20for%20New%20York%20or%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20dynamic%20has%20changed.%20Paris%20has%20undergone%20a%20quiet%20quant%20renaissance%2C%20with%20firms%20like%20Squarepoint%20and%20Qube%20Research%20building%20major%20presences%20in%20the%20city%2C%20and%20US%20heavyweights%20including%20Point72's%20Cubist%20group%20and%20Citadel%20expanding%20as%20well.%20The%20competition%20now%20spans%20every%20function%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20investment%20research%20but%20also%20HR%2C%20technology%2C%20and%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20two%20world-class%20peers%20emerge%20in%20Paris%2C%20created%20competition%20across%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20firm%2C%20which%20we%20were%20not%20used%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20Jordan%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20that's%20not%20bad%20because%20it%20sharpens%20you%20up%2C%20and%20it%20creates%20a%20pool%20of%20talent%20also%20in%20the%20city%20that%20didn't%20exist%20before.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a6a57f95-05a1-4e96-8515-d8bb1a5c583c%5C%22%3EWinning%20in%20the%20long%20run%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20amount%20of%20cultural%20hygiene%20or%20philosophical%20purity%20matters%20if%20a%20hedge%20fund%20doesn't%20make%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20CFM%20has%20been%20on%20a%20hot%20streak%2C%20with%20its%20flagship%20Stratus%20fund%2C%20now%20closed%20to%20new%20investors%2C%20earning%20double-digits%20the%20past%20three%20years.%20Last%20month%2C%20it%20returned%20%242%20billion%20to%20investors%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20preserve%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECFM%20has%20pulled%20higher%20capacity%20strategies%20from%20the%20%26quot%3Bmain%20battleship%26quot%3B%20into%20new%20standalone%20funds.%20The%20Cumulus%20fund%20launched%20two%20years%20ago%20and%20is%20closing%20in%20on%20%242%20billion%20in%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20understanding%20at%20CFM%20is%20that%20this%20success%20is%20a%20direct%20result%20of%20its%20philosophies%20that%20run%20counter%20to%20industry%20norms.%20Could%20it%20take%20a%20more%20cutthroat%20approach%20and%20maximize%20profits%3F%20Not%20without%20sacrificing%20performance%20in%20the%20long%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20developed%20this%20culture%20over%20time%20and%20believe%20it%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20advance%20our%20understanding%20of%20markets%20and%20sustainably%20deliver%20investment%20outperformance%2C%26quot%3B%20Jordan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrench-hedge-fund-cfm-growth-spurt-unique-culture-2025-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1765022646000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69331e4a7ecd1d1da66306da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrench-hedge-fund-cfm-growth-spurt-unique-culture-2025-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hedge%20fund%20Capital%20Fund%20Management%20defies%20industry%20norms.%20It's%20on%20a%20growth%20tear%20anyway%20%E2%80%94%20performing%20so%20well%20it's%20handing%20money%20back%20to%20investors.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22amorrell%40businessinsider.com%20(Alex%20Morrell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrench-hedge-fund-cfm-growth-spurt-unique-culture-2025-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine%20showed%20the%20UK%20its%20classic%20'tactically%20safe'%20trench-clearing%20methods%20don't%20work%20in%20chaotic%2C%20booby-trapped%20trenches%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20figure%20in%20camouflage%20gear%20and%20a%20helmet%20runs%20in%20a%20shallow%2C%20muddy%20trench%20with%20another%20figure%20leaning%20over%20the%20side%20of%20it%20in%20the%20background%20and%20another%20walking%2C%20all%20under%20a%20grey%20sky%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6931948304d0f0a114f163df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkraine's%20east%20has%20become%20full%20of%20trenches%2C%20which%20are%20key%20to%20keeping%20soldiers%20in%20alive%20in%20a%20flat%20landscape%20packed%20with%20drones%20and%20artillery.%3Cp%3ERoman%20PILIPEY%20%2F%20AFP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20UK%20had%20assumed%20trench%20building%20and%20clearing%20to%20be%20quite%20clean%20and%20surgical%2C%20an%20officer%20who%20trained%20Ukrainians%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20in%20Ukraine's%20fight%2C%20they're%20uneven%20